			"[On-Play]: Reveal the top 2 cards of your deck. Add 1 <Arm> SIGNI and 1 <Weapon> SIGNI form among them to your hand, and put the rest on top of your deck in any order. If you did not add any SIGNI to your hand this way, down this SIGNI."
